modName: FalmerBanes - Illiana - Witch of the Rift
summary: Illiana is the non-replacer version of my Gothic Illia mod. This is really a two part mod.  This mod introduces a new follower named Illiana into your game plus a revamped Alchemist\'s Shack that can be used as a tiny player home. Dragonborn DLC is REQUIRED for the main and optional versions! Edit: I added two non-DLC dependent Skyrim versions.
